metadata.name: Bugha Bucks (#1/555)
metadata.description:
VeeFriends Mini Drops Bugha Rookie Card - Created By [VeeFriends](https://veefriends.com) and [Bugha](https://www.instagram.com/bugha/) VeeFriends is thrilled to partner with Bugha, one of the most famous gamers in the world, to create his Rookie NFT card. The original owner of this NFT also received an Anthros chair, a luxury chair from company that is revolutionizing the way we sit. This token is a part of the Gift Goat series and a VeeFriends Mini Drop collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain. 'Bugha Bucks' is gift #10 of 18. Bugha Rookie Card is an edition of 555 unique NFTs, created by artist Gilang Bogy, the famous artist behind the first sports card NFT collection on the blockchain "Wrapped Strikers", VaynerSports Pass, and most recently VeeFriends Iconics. This NFT does not grant you previous or future gifts from the Gift Goat Gifting Experience. For more information on the Gift Goat Series, please visit: [https://veefriends.com/giftgoat](https://veefriends.com/giftgoat) Bugha [Twitch](https://twitch.tv/bugha)
